  <p>Check <a href="/availability">here.</a></p>
  <p class="question">Is your meat grass-fed?</p>
  <p>If it is, it will say in the description. However, most steak enthusiasts actually believe that grass-fed meat doesn't taste as good as corn-fed meat.</p>

